sentences.sentence: To spread jam, butter, honey, etc. on a piece of bread (une tartine).
sentences.translation: 在面包上涂抹果酱、黄油、蜂蜜等(涂有或供涂黄油等的面包片)。

sentences.sentence: The products do not comply with the relevant national standard UNE 20315.
sentences.translation: 该产品不符合国家有关标准的新英格兰20315。

sentences.sentence: To explain how this could all possibly happens would be not wild (folles) but a folly (une folie).
sentences.translation: 要解释这一切为何发生，不是疯了(folles)，应是愚昧(une folie)。
